==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: garand
<hw>garand</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[From the inventor, <person>John C.
<etsep>Garand</etsep></person>.]</ety> <def>A semiautomatic rifle, also
called the <altname>M-1</altname>, used by soldiers of the U. S. army in
World War II and Korea. It was the standard weapon issued to
infantrymen.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> Garand rifle, M-1, M-1 rifle.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source> <source>+PJC</source>]</p>

